{"tid":1637371,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我就係推英文台既搞手，有咩想講既入黎","createTime":"2019-10-08T03:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T13:04:13.000Z","uid":130079,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4d23cf0073b7ddf17e43a717bcfb64c03289eb7f","tid":1637371,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:19:59.000Z","msg":"係，我就係一個人洗足一個星期英文台post既人。<br />\n想大家入黎一齊傾，World都係我諗連仔既回應<br />\n<br />\n最開頭既諗法就係，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">外國既港人都可以文宣戰出一分力，同連接twitter文宣平台</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行動上整體建議：<br />\n<br />\n限制<br />\n如果大家認同下面既，就希望大家幫手一齊做，<br />\n（唔使樣樣都認同既）<br />\n<br />\n-中文post，負評，report，不推文回覆<br />\n<br />\n-中文字地方語系同上處理<br />\n-港式英文一樣處理(e.g. diu lei lo mo)<br />\n<br />\n-中英雙語ok，回覆雙語/英文<br />\n<br />\n-外語系暫時冷處理，因為一個台俾大量大家睇唔明既post洗版唔係好事，呢個我諗大家比較有爭議<br />\n（或者開post既人以<span style=\"color: red;\">英文開首做warning</span>,話外語討論有高風險國家級煽動，滋生攻擊醜化示威者同市民既內容）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出post:<br />\n-將完全confirm既消息轉化為英文post<br />\n-精選高汁post去twitter<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">外國巴打<br />\n1.twitter俾其他人知，叫佢地裝app<br />\n2.教佢地註冊<br />\n3. 幫手制作英文文宣<br />\n4.教佢地點出post<br />\n5.重點邀請外國記者（可實名）註冊發問<br />\n6. 當然叫政客裝，跟蹤時事<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"975540ff578338f03119167a92c1a5b4236a9a29","tid":1637371,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e29adcdeff7285a7cab2b894e870e1a412cc008","tid":1637371,"uid":330274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d8813e028a99b042c9225b657c0f6752ebc296","tid":1637371,"uid":152594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:41:22.000Z","msg":"英文五毛遠遠比廣東話五毛多，但英文連登仔女又比起廣東話連登仔女少<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢樣野大家點睇？點拆好？"},{"pid":"b092d51e80e73544b1e5ec21f94abcb5b6ee884b","tid":1637371,"uid":130079,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1d8813e028a99b042c9225b657c0f6752ebc296","tid":1637371,"uid":152594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:41:22.000Z","msg":"英文五毛遠遠比廣東話五毛多，但英文連登仔女又比起廣東話連登仔女少<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢樣野大家點睇？點拆好？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:49:58.000Z","msg":"1.唔好放棄，我係例子<br />\n我一個人洗超過成個星期英文台，將兩個月既post洗上頂，最後一日坐係到洗12個鐘post先出到world。五毛為錢你為理念，差好遠<br />\n<br />\n2.twitter都夠多，但twitter既文宣未放棄，唔該自己都堅持。<br />\n<br />\n3.煲得太同靚既文宣就係有激烈討論，5毛係幫到手<br />\n<br />\n4.開post貼張燒黨旗圖，佢地每推一次<br />\n你就拎燒旗圖覆"},{"pid":"a8204c36110b969929ac73edb2a57df6dd43b7e2","tid":1637371,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:55:10.000Z","msg":"終於開左 World channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾時開埋 Home channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d4beefb5d9fca6552ca95fbb4e732734baf30d","tid":1637371,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:29:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a3ec6bdbc5d7fea29a6cd1bcd3d06aa0662b8004","tid":1637371,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:54:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9e4da05bfdc8b1a8215c1f7bf85d418901678141","tid":1637371,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:05:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1bd0437e81467740b9638364fc5456613fc80d2b","tid":1637371,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:06:49.000Z","msg":"盡力幫手 但係自己P牌 諸多限制"},{"pid":"94f9ed450fc2fa9d75d8ba694d892757ef55f5a7","tid":1637371,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bd0437e81467740b9638364fc5456613fc80d2b","tid":1637371,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:06:49.000Z","msg":"盡力幫手 但係自己P牌 諸多限制"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:33:49.000Z","msg":"Thanks"},{"pid":"a50a0fcb36abae689ff81e7ba46f7127ef5bff4b","tid":1637371,"uid":327193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:36:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e867ba30cd96d7b8fd30d6e4d46066c5b1f6a9a","tid":1637371,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:06:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"025f0093bb269600d2ce54ff45c926600efb8fc7","tid":1637371,"uid":141266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:10:10.000Z","msg":"Pushhh"},{"pid":"2dd98d4dd916d981fadfb390309ab5b347dcc9ee","tid":1637371,"uid":27894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:16:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b224c8a31b513c174d1906fb03c5a6c9fbf50655","tid":1637371,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T20:05:25.000Z","msg":"為左防止外語五毛, 不如將world轉成英文台算<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1637935\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1637935</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"abd031d48c85309364f48ae3b04a1b7a5cdc5633","tid":1637371,"uid":271130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T20:20:48.000Z","msg":"你可能好心做左壞事<br />\n<br />\n本身cc台都唔係時時夠人 成日比人帶風<br />\n英文台 可想而知<br />\n<br />\n再者如果原意係想外國人了解多d連登香港式culture同新聞真相，佢地唔識睇中文就己經好難明"},{"pid":"b890fda5e16f47a6bfeaf28a10c9c89940f